{"tid":959100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"氣溫急降 天文台考慮今晚發寒冷天氣警告","createTime":"2018-12-28T10:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T00:23:24.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae001f64f62bdd1222ef3b9787960a8ef0f486e8","tid":959100,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"【即時天氣】氣溫急降 天文台考慮今晚發寒冷天氣警告<br />\n<br />\n【17:40】預計明日氣溫急降，天文台考慮今晚發出入冬以來首個寒冷天氣警告<br />\n【17:00】現時氣溫18.8&deg;C，相對濕度65%。<br />\n<br />\n影響華南的冬季季候風正逐漸增強。在下午4時，位於菲律賓以東的熱帶低氣壓集結在馬尼拉之東南偏東約830公里，預料向西北偏西移動，時速約12公里，移向菲律賓中部。<br />\n<br />\n天文台預測今日晚間漸轉多雲。明日天氣轉冷，市區氣溫介乎12至16&deg;C，新界再低兩三度，日間部分時間天色明朗。吹和緩至清勁北至東北風，明日離岸及高地間中吹強風。<br />\n<br />\n展望：隨後數日持續寒冷，風勢頗大。下週初至中期有幾陣雨。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"1e849cbae2fd9635156d1a62638ea3c855fe4bbc","tid":959100,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"呢個post 主題冇日子, 將會好撚環保"},{"pid":"4b42f658d174004b335834422472fe9162ea5781","tid":959100,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59077997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59077997&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3e8da43d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59077997&h=c78dcc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59077997</a>"},{"pid":"f4b46c1836b3548003cbd26a497383d940925da4","tid":959100,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T00:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}